metadata.name: Steamy window
metadata.description:
This photo of a steamy window was taken on Christmas day 2019 on the Ceintuurbaan in Amsterdam stays one of my favorites. Maybe it is because of the blurriness witch creates room in my head to let my imagination flow, or maybe every time other aspects in this multi-layered picture come to the attention. 

This picture is part of the singles collection. Here are the pictures collected which doesn't really fit in with the rest, but maybe because of that deserve special attention.

F-stop: f/2.8
exposure: 1/1000
35mm lens
size: 5043x3362
